description: Promotes clear and meaningful code comments.
globs: ["*.py", "*.ts", "*.tsx", "*.js", "*.jsx"]
alwaysApply: false
---
Use professional, easy-to-understand comments.

- Explain the *why*, not just the *what*, especially for complex or non-obvious logic.
- Keep comments concise and focused.
- Ensure comments are kept up-to-date as the code evolves.
- Avoid redundant comments that merely restate the code. 